Michael Shane https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Shane 0 Michael Shane (May 4, 1927 — February 22, 1994) was an American lawyer and actor. Born in Cleveland, Ohio, he attended Glenville High School. While earning his undergraduate and law degrees at Ohio State University, he performed as a stand-up comic at local nightclubs.
